            "title": "韓股收市微跌",
            "description": "<div class=\"article-body\">\n<p class=\"font-size-scaler-control\" data-font=\"16\">南韓股市微跌。</p>\n<p class=\"font-size-scaler-control\" data-font=\"16\">首爾綜合指數收報2592點，跌1點。</p>\n<p class=\"font-size-scaler-control\" data-font=\"16\">全星期計，韓股跌逾1%。</p>\n</div>",
